law.catch_line: Administrative mission units of museum -- Associate directors.
law.text: The purposes of KRS 146.650 to 146.666 shall be carried out through the operation of mission units. When the Kentucky Natural History Museum is established, the mission units shall become administrative units of the museum. Each unit shall be managed by an associate director.
law.history: Created 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 329, sec. 6, effective July 14, 2000.
